.repopilot-patches/

docs/demos/*.tape
!docs/demos/02-review.tape
!docs/demos/03-agent-review.tape
!docs/demos/04-java-agent-review.tape
docs/demos/*.log

# Real-repo validation zoo: repos are cloned here on demand, never committed.
# Only tests/zoo/manifest.toml + tests/zoo/snapshots/*.json are tracked.
/.zoo/
